data.description: This one year old townhome style condo is ready for you to call it home! This corner unit is almost 1700 sq ft of finished living area and offers many features to include, 3 spacious bedrooms, 2.5 baths. bedroom level laundry, main area entry, lots of NATURAL LIGHT due to additional windows with the home being an end unit, personal balcony of the kitchen on the front, your own garage on the lower level with your own driveway and more. This townhome is equipped with smart home capabilities to include EERO Wi-Fi (on every floor), Ring Doorbell, Smart Network, Smart Locks, an alarm Security Kit, Flo by Moen water leak detector, Smart Garage Control. Condo fees include water/sewer, trash and snow removal. Convenient daily commuting and is right next to the Rippon Landing VRE Station and also just minutes to I-95, shopping, dining, recreation, and the added convenience of living near Stonebridge TownCenter & Wegmans. Centrally located to the historic town of Occoquan, outdoor activities at Featherstone National Wildlife Refuge as well as Neabsco Regional Park along the Potomac River. Check out the floor plans and virtual tour. Schedule your showing today!
